article.description: — Isaiah Powell had 17 points and seven rebounds as Vermont topped Evansville 58-49 in the Gulf Coast Showcase on Tuesday.
article.headline: Powell scores 17 to lift Vermont past Evansville 58-49
article.linkText: Powell scores 17 to lift Vermont past Evansville 58-49
article.story: ESTERO, Fla. -- — Isaiah Powell had 17 points and seven rebounds as Vermont topped Evansville 58-49 in the Gulf Coast Showcase on Tuesday. Ben Shungu had 12 points for Vermont (4-2). Jawaun Newton had 16 points for the Purple Aces (2-5). Noah Frederking added seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
